** Why is this an exciting opportunity? **

At Atturra, an Australian-owned ASX-listed advisory and IT solutions provider,
we have a team of over 700 professionals working across Australia, New
Zealand, and Singapore. Our diverse and dynamic team is united by our passion
for innovation, using our expertise to leverage technology for business
transformation.

As part of our Cloud Business Solutions team, we have a strong partnership
with Microsoft. This allows us to leverage their cutting-edge technologies and
resources to deliver exceptional solutions to our clients. Our partnership
provides us with unique insights, training, and support, keeping us at the
forefront of technological innovation.

Joining our team means you’ll become part of a community of change-makers who
are redefining the future through technology. You'll be able to make a real
impact, working on exciting projects that challenge conventional thinking and
drive meaningful change for our clients.

At Atturra, we foster a collaborative, inclusive work environment that
encourages growth, learning, and professional development. We value diversity
and empower our employees to reach their full potential.

Joining Atturra provides a strong foundation to fulfil your career ambitions.
If you're ready to be part of a dynamic organisation shaping the digital
landscape, Atturra is the place for you.

